{"tid":905613,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗新盤】尚悅．嶺今賣102伙 暫沽6伙","createTime":"2018-11-17T09:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T18:22:36.000Z","uid":62935,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0716cf36dfc9ae81808cdf836226038fbfad63d3","tid":905613,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T09:21:31.000Z","msg":"恒地(012)旗下元朗尚悅．嶺，今日下午2時於尖沙咀美麗華廣場以先到先得形式推售102伙，折實入場費326.5萬元。項目日前加推51伙，實用面積255至270方呎，售價加價2%，折實入場費由385.2萬元起。市場指該盤暫時售出6伙。<br />\n<br />\n中原地產亞太區副主席兼住宅部總裁陳永傑表示，今日有兩個新界西新盤同時開售，兩盤反應均一般，因為客源與居屋重疊，而他們目標是搶400萬元的單位，「高少少都唔買」，故影響銷情，料即日賣出10伙內。對於一手後市，他指現時發展商推售新盤時，提供的優惠等，都在不斷測試市場可接受的程度，相信一手未來較高位下調10%至15%，才能有效去貨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他又指，昨日公佈的中原城市領先指數CCL，連跌7周，比高位跌3 %，相信年尾樓價再下調3%至5%。成交量方面，11月應會手較10月好，因為二手業主願意降價，較合理價減5%至10%，可有承接。他補充，現時樓市只是處於整固階段，未屬轉勢，後市還看中美貿易糾紛是否可解決。<br />\n<br />\n記者 葉煜燊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181117/58925211\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58925211&d=Aqh3AviE8OJ44wl0vSHkdJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=3260b93b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58925211&h=9bfd6c80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181117/58925211</a>"},{"pid":"8ffe95b86932c3ec930725fab5277e97833fd97f","tid":905613,"uid":112720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T09:37:23.000Z","msg":"剛需呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d3d7ea84a4645133c0b5d2c7661be5e2b8b591","tid":905613,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quo